<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-CRIME-REVIEW-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
STORM WARNING: THE COMING CRIME WAVE IS WASHED UP 
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(bl) 
 By JACQUES STEINBERG    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
