<HEADLINE>
WAR WITHOUT CASUALTIES: AVOIDING LOSSES IS ONE THING, WINNING IS
ANOTHER
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By SERGE SCHMEMANN    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``I want you to remember that no bastard ever won a war by dying
