<HEADLINE>
CAMBODIA'S BYGONES RESIST BEING BYGONES
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By SETH MYDANS    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   SIHANOUKVILLE, Cambodia _ As two Khmer Rouge leaders accused of
