diarrhea. On others, it strikes only after eating a piece of
chocolate or something containing milk. Her symptoms include
bloating, gas and abdominal pain, sometimes so severe that the only
relief is staying in bed or close to a bathroom. It turned out to
be irritable bowel syndrome, for which there are no answers. By
SYLVIA WOOD.
