</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH-REHNQUIST (Washington) _ The stern, no-nonsense manner
of Chief Justice William Rehnquist is likely to be his greatest
impact on the Clinton impeachment trial. By Anne E. Kornblut. 1480
words.
</P>
<P>
   PROFILE-WATTS (Washington) -- US Rep. J.C. Watts of Oklahoma has
parlayed his civil rights background, fame as a football player,
and robust espousal of conservative positions to become the only
black person in a leadership position in Congress. By Louise d.
Palmer. 1350 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
