<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-04 13:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7128 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BOOK-FATIGUE-BOS &LR;      01-04 1271
