<P>
   EYE SCOOPS: OONA O'NEILL CHAPLIN'S LIFE; DESIGNER OLIVIER
THEYSKENS MEETS FAIRY GODMOTHER
</P>
<P>
   TREND WATCH: DANDY WRAPPERS
</P>
<P>
   TROPICAL PUNCH
</P>
<P>
   BEAUTY WATCH: JUNIOR LEAGUE
</P>
