   But the turmoil in financial markets hurt everybody to some
degree. Bonuses were down sharply, hard-boiled eggs compared with
the golden ones of the preceding few years.
</P>
<P>
   The share price of many financial companies fell by half to
two-thirds between July and September, crushing the value of
