pressure is really on, because spring is when President Clinton
goes into heat.''
</P>
<P>
   ``Republican Senator Orrin Hatch is now admitting that the
Senate doesn't have the two-thirds vote to remove President Clinton
from office. So instead, they're going to get really drunk and T.P.
the White House.''
</P>
<P>
   ``Barbara Walters says she's met with Monica Lewinsky twice, and
she found her very warm. Mostly because they spent the time
spooning.''
</P>
<P>
   ``Pop star Jewel says she's a big fan of Marilyn Manson and
she'd love to do a duet with him. Meanwhile, Marilyn Manson says
he'd love to shave Jewel's skull and tattoo a pentagram on her
forehead.''
</P>
<P>
   ``Once again, President Clinton will spend his New Year's
weekend attending a seminar dedicated to personal growth.
Apparently, last year there was an awkward moment because President
Clinton asked someone to touch his personal growth.''
</P>
<P>
   ``According to federal laws, if President Clinton is removed
from office, he will lose his Secret Service protection. President
Clinton is very nervous because right now the Secret Service is the
only thing protecting him from Hillary.''
</P>
