<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-04 17:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7573 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DOLE05-COX     01-04 0627
