</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH (Washington) _ Sen. Trent Lott returns to the Capitol
and prepares a series of meetings with Republicans throughout
Tuesday as senators continue to search for the compromise that
would allow them to end an impeachment trial quickly. By Alison
Mitchell. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``w'' news file.)
</P>
