QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-NY-SUBWAY-VICTIM-NYT, which
moved in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``She was the kind of person who would have helped the kind of
person who did this.''
</P>
<P>
   _RALPH T. WEBDALE JR., whose sister, Kendra, was killed Sunday
when a man pushed her in front of a subway train in New York City.
</P>
</TEXT>
