<P>
   (NYT18) UNDATED -- Jan. 4, 1999 -- NY-SUBWAY-VICTIM-2, 1-4 --
Kendra Webdale in an undated photo released by her family. Webdale,
32, died on Sunday after being pushed in front of a subway train in
New York by a man with a history of mental illness. In a city that
has seen violent crimes take a startling drop in recent years,
Webdale's death was a reminder of how random acts of violence can
shake a city's psyche. (New York Times Photo)
